You are the iOS developer for a BM (business model) migration. The app is transitioning from tier-based subscription (free/basic/premium) to an ad-based model with a single Pro subscription.

**Goal**: All users get 200 requests/day. Reward ads grant +10 bonus requests (max 5 ads/day). Pro subscription removes ads. AdMob SDK integration for banner + reward ads.

